Add initial project structure with configuration files and dataset metadata
- Created .gitignore to exclude unnecessary files. - Added .python-version to specify Python version. - Introduced pyproject.toml for project metadata and dependencies. - Updated README.md with project description. - Added dataset metadata for the Discogs Music Database. - Included various documentation files related to Kaggle and Discogs API. - Set up Visual Studio Code settings for project development. - Added initial dataset files in DuckDB and SQLite formats for analytics.
